data.title: Ramsey Chandler
data.text:
Position: Designer/Writer

Class: Sophomore

Majors: History, Studio Art

Hometown: Auburn, AL

Ramsey Chandler is a sophomore at UA double-majoring in History and Studio Art with a concentration in Digital Media. She has a passion for all things art, film, and music. When sheâ€™s not at Woods Hall, you can typically find her at the movies, attending the concerts of her favorite bands, or at the gym. Ramsey also enjoys traveling, reading, and spending time with her family and friends. Ramsey hopes to one-day land a career working with Disney. The biggest obstacle she has had to overcome while attending U of A is being from Auburn.
